6 An Act relating to education; amending 70 O.S. 2021,
Section 6-127A, which relates to public school
7 paraprofessionals; exempting certain
paraprofessionals from certain educational
8 requirements; exempting certain teachers from certain
additional educational requirements; providing for
9 codification; providing an effective date; and
